titles.title: Brief conversation about clam[m]ing between Ed and Flourence Sigo of Kamilchee Bay recorded January 18, 1968; Love song sung by FS (2/1/68) (following short violin piece).

descriptions.description: Contents: 1 – Ed (Suquamish) and Flourence (Puyallup) Sigo – Brief conversation about clam[m]ing between Ed and Flourence Sigo of Kamilchee Bay recorded January 18, 1968 Love song sung by FS (2/1/68) (following short violin piece) From Thom Hess Collection, Ethnomusicology Archives (UWEA 95-19.21) University of Washington, Seattle
